name: Street Fighter II DASH
summary:
In the name of destiny, they continue their fight. That glimmer in their eyes - is it the glow of victory or the brutal ember of defeat? 
 
Following the great success of the world famous predecessor, this game push the enthusiam for this series forward anothor peak. 
 
STREET FIGHTER II DASH: with its all new features and images, it will never fall short of your high expectations.
